\text{Time} = 2\frac{3}{4}\text{ hours} = 2 + \frac{3}{4} = \frac{8}{4} + \frac{3}{4} = \frac{11}{4}\text{ hours}
\]

\[
\text{Distance} = 50 \text{ mph} \times \frac{11}{4}\text{ h}
= \frac{50 \times 11}{4}
= \frac{550}{4}
= 137.5
\]

Express \(137.5\) as a mixed number:

\[
137.5 = 137 \frac{1}{2}
